{"sections": {"main": {"type": "main-product--default", "blocks": {"header": {"type": "product_header", "settings": {"show_divider": true, "show_vendor": true, "show_sku": true, "show_discount": true, "discount_format": "percent_off", "show_product_rating": false, "show_sale_badge": true, "show_custom_badges": true}}, "description": {"type": "description", "settings": {"title": "", "title_tag": "h3", "text_font_class": "fs-body-100", "column_placement": "right", "display_as_collapsible_row": false, "expand_by_default": false, "icon": "none"}}, "variant_picker": {"type": "variant_picker", "settings": {"variant_popup_option": "Size", "variant_popup_icon": "none", "variant_popup_text": "Size guide", "variant_popup_page": "", "swatch_size": "medium", "chip_layout": "natural"}}, "buy_buttons": {"type": "buy_buttons", "settings": {"show_dynamic_checkout": true, "enable_sticky_atc_bar_desktop": true, "enable_sticky_atc_bar_mobile": true, "divider_width": "border--thin"}}, "callouts": {"type": "product_callouts", "settings": {"title": "", "title_tag": "h3", "add_box": true, "add_dividers": true, "icon_1": "leaf", "text_1": "<p><strong>14k Gold</strong> \u00b7 Freshwater Pearl \u00b7 Ethiopian Opal \u00b7 Diamond</p>", "icon_2": "measuring-tape", "text_2": "<p><strong>~1mm</strong> band width \u00b7 Sizes 3\u20139</p>", "icon_3": "stiletto", "text_3": "<p>Handcrafted in NYC</p>", "icon_4": "moving-truck", "text_4": "<p>Free insured shipping \u00b7 1-year warranty</p>", "icon_5": "bill", "text_5": "<p><strong>Made to order</strong> \u00b7 3\u20134 week production</p>", "icon_6": "none", "text_6": "", "display_as_collapsible_row": false, "expand_by_default": false, "icon": "none"}}, "share": {"type": "share", "settings": {}}}, "block_order": ["header", "description", "variant_picker", "buy_buttons", "callouts", "share"], "settings": {"enable_sticky_product_details": true, "show_breadcrumbs": false, "show_navigation_buttons": false, "auto_collapse_rows": false, "show_featured_media_first": false, "gallery_style": "list", "gallery_style_mobile": "carousel", "gallery_size": "large", "gallery_overflow": "3", "enable_video_looping": true, "enable_product_lightbox": true, "image_aspect_ratio": "portrait", "enable_multiple_variant_media": false, "enable_mobile_carousel_looping": true, "show_mobile_carousel_images_full_width": true, "hide_mobile_carousel_dots": false, "enable_gift_card_recipient": true, "enable_animation": true}}, "product_tabs": {"type": "product-tabs", "blocks": {"tab_description": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Description", "heading_column_1": "What Makes It Special", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>Delicate and luminous, a sculptural arrangement of four different materials on the slenderest possible band. Aurivelle combines pearl, opal, and diamond \u2014 three kinds of light in one tiny composition.</p><p>The Ethiopian opal is the surprise: it fires with internal color that shifts from green to orange to blue. Paired with the steady glow of pearl and the sharp flash of diamond (0.03ct), Aurivelle packs an extraordinary amount of visual interest into a ring that weighs almost nothing.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_details": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Details & Materials", "heading_column_1": "Specifications", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<ul><li><strong>Material:</strong> 14k yellow gold</li><li><strong>Stones:</strong> Freshwater pearls (5.5mm \u00d7 1, 4.5mm \u00d7 1), Ethiopian opal (0.22 ct), diamond (0.03 ct)</li><li><strong>Band Width:</strong> ~1mm</li><li><strong>Sizes:</strong> 3 through 9 (half sizes available)</li><li><strong>Collection:</strong> Echoes</li></ul>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_care": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Care", "heading_column_1": "Jewelry Care", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p><strong>Gold & Pearl Rings:</strong> Remove before washing hands, swimming, or exercise. Store in the provided pouch. The delicate band benefits from careful handling. Wipe with a soft cloth after wearing. Avoid perfume, chlorine, and harsh chemicals.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_shipping": {"type": "two_column_tab", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Shipping & Returns", "content_vertical_alignment": "top", "column_spacing": 48, "heading_column_1": "Made to Order", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>Every piece is handcrafted to order in NYC. Please allow 3\u20134 weeks for production. Free insured shipping on all orders. Signature required on delivery. You'll receive email updates during production and tracking when your piece ships.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text", "heading_column_2": "Returns & Warranty", "heading_font_class_column_2": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_2": "h3", "text_column_2": "<p>All sales are final \u2014 each piece is made specifically for you. 1-year warranty covers manufacturing defects. If your piece arrives damaged, contact us within 14 days with photos for repair or replacement.</p>", "page_for_content_column_2": "", "custom_liquid_column_2": "", "text_font_class_column_2": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_2": 100, "image_position_column_2": "above_text"}}}, "block_order": ["tab_description", "tab_details", "tab_care", "tab_shipping"], "settings": {"tab_alignment": "left", "tab_spacing": 40, "font_choice": "ff-heading", "tab_font_size": "fs-body-150", "auto_collapse_rows": false, "background_color": "", "text_color": "#000000", "enable_animation": true, "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-bottom-only"}}, "multi-column": {"type": "multi-column", "blocks": {}, "block_order": [], "disabled": true, "settings": {"title": "", "heading_tag": "h2", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-3-base", "subheading": "", "heading_alignment": "left", "content_vertical_alignment": "center", "content_background_padding": "large", "columns": "3", "column_spacing": 4, "row_spacing": 28, "column_alignment": "center", "enable_slider_mobile": false, "columns_mobile": "1", "column_spacing_mobile": 4, "row_spacing_mobile": 4, "column_alignment_mobile": "center", "background_behind_columns": false, "background_color": "#f5f3f0", "text_color": "#3d352f", "button_background_color": "#000000", "button_text_color": "#ffffff", "enable_animation": true, "divider_style": "none", "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-top-bottom"}}, "image-hero": {"type": "image-hero", "blocks": {"accent": {"type": "accent", "settings": {"accent": "ECHOES COLLECTION"}}, "heading": {"type": "heading", "settings": {"title": "Aurivelle", "heading_tag": "h2", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-display-2"}}}, "block_order": ["accent", "heading"], "settings": {"image_aspect": "custom", "desktop_height": 60, "mobile_height": 65, "focal_point": "center", "mobile_focal_point": "center", "media_link": "", "text_position": "flex-end_flex-end", "text_position_mobile": "center_center", "text_color": "#f5f5f5", "button_background_color": "#ffffff", "button_